Moggido Maven Repository is supported by DropBox. See https://www.dropbox.com.
Ask for developers for a settings.xml with username and password.

Default setting:
Windows:
Dropbox folder at location c:\My Dropbox

To deploy artifacts not generated with maven, use the following command:

  mvn deploy:deploy-file -Durl=file://C:/My%20Dropbox/Public/(snapshots|releases)
						 -DrepositoryId=moggido-repo-(releases|snapshots) 
                         -Dfile=(location to your file)
                         -DgroupId=(groupId of deployed artifact)
                         -DartifactId=(artifactId of deployed artifact)
                         -Dversion=(version of deployed artifact)                        
                         -Dpackaging=jar 